a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).

a.txt[1P.txtR.txtE.txtA.txtD.txtM.txtE.txt
The means and variances of helpfulness values will significantly differ between different products and different customers. Some products/customers tend to be more popular and prolific, thus resulting in a much greater size and value of raw helpfulness values to work with. Others tend to be far and few inbetween, with some customers/products being very unpopular and only having one review and a minimal helpfulness value (in which case, mean and variance also doesn't really matter).
